- ## Specification
#Specification #Quality #Challenges #NonFunctional #Requirements #Software #Engineering 
Requirements  volatility has great impact on the cost, the schedule and the  quality of final product. Due to requirements volatility many  projects fail and some are completed partially. Requirements  volatility cannot be overcome fully but we can minimize it with  some requirement measures or metrics
